"""Functional tests for the AuthN routes (signup/login/logout/set-password/me).

These exercise the routers via a probe app that mounts the auth router and overrides
``control_session`` onto a real test control DB (create_all — Task 7 alembic deferred). Signup is
routing-agnostic in Phase 1 (``register_tenant``+``activate`` in the control plane only; no physical
per-tenant DB), so these tests need only the control engine — no provisioning machinery.

Outcome-space: founder→admin happy path, no-enumeration login/collision failures, logout/login
roundtrip, **login mints a FRESH session (fixation)**, single-use set-password that **invalidates
all sessions**, and the **fail-closed signup gate** (prod→404, staging+empty→403, staging+match→201,
dev→201).
"""

